        ":::{.solution}\n",
        "a) $P(\\text{both red}) = \\frac{5}{8} \\times \\frac{4}{7} = \\frac{20}{56} = \\frac{5}{14}$\n",
        "\n",
        "b) $P(\\text{red then blue}) = \\frac{5}{8} \\times \\frac{3}{7} = \\frac{15}{56}$\n",
