        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Law of Total Probability {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        ":::{.definition}\n",
        "**üéØ Definition**\n",
        "\n",
        "If events $B_1, B_2, \\ldots, B_n$ form a partition of the sample space, then:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$P(A) = P(A|B_1)P(B_1) + P(A|B_2)P(B_2) + \\cdots + P(A|B_n)P(B_n)$$\n",
        ":::"
      ],
